snippet.title: Time From Earth (Playdate) - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Find out more: pixel-ghost.itch.io

The year is 2052...Following the Global Peace Treaty and formation of the Global Space Agency, Physis 5 is on a mission to discover our next home...

Time From Earth is a narrative adventure exclusively for the Playdate console.
